    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/e683a053a485eedf4cec9ae2f8989908.avif?t=1682351063\" width=640 height=107 /></span><br>Remote Planets is a cute, relaxing puzzle game set in a mysterious alien galaxy. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/193e7723625bc954978613fc34fe0ad4.poster.avif?t=1682351063\" width=498 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/193e7723625bc954978613fc34fe0ad4.webm?t=1682351063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/193e7723625bc954978613fc34fe0ad4.mp4?t=1682351063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/52953707138949c74855b2aaf49da321.avif?t=1682351063\" width=640 height=107 /></span><br>Explore the colorful world, solve logic challenges using unique mechanics and help the friendly cast of villagers restore power to their homes. Reshape the level space with the help of mysterious alien technology. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/d7883b3ac5a2fac6480739f0cdb7cf20.poster.avif?t=1682351063\" width=498 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/d7883b3ac5a2fac6480739f0cdb7cf20.webm?t=1682351063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/d7883b3ac5a2fac6480739f0cdb7cf20.mp4?t=1682351063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/840ebb66f5d39bd0cca232fd0c261319.avif?t=1682351063\" width=640 height=107 /></span><br>The game contains:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> over 120 challenging hand-crafted puzzles<br></li><li> multiple unique mechanics blending together<br></li><li> a colorful, welcoming alien world<br></li><li> a cast of funny, friendly characters <br></li><li> a relaxing, chill ambient soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/d9dbea7149aab2d783329a9632703ffa.poster.avif?t=1682351063\" width=498 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/d9dbea7149aab2d783329a9632703ffa.webm?t=1682351063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2197020/extras/d9dbea7149aab2d783329a9632703ffa.mp4?t=1682351063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
